description:
What would you do if you were met with the question - 'What doest thou here Elijah?', if you were not following God's will for your life? John Loughborough was met with this question by Ellen White, as she found him working in a store. After this, John renewed his commitment to service and to God, and returned to Michigan with Ellen White. He went on to become a powerful missionary for the church. 

To find out more about J.N. Loughborough visit our website to read our extended article on him.
